short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a customizable equalizer to YouTube videos.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YouTube Equalizer is a Chrome extension that adds a powerful, customizable equalizer directly to YouTube. Enhance your listening experience by adjusting audio frequencies to suit your preferences.

Features:
Audio Visualizer
Multiple Band Options: 5, 10, 20, and 31-band equalizer options.
Intuitive sliders for precise audio control.
Dynamic adjustments with smooth frequency transitions.
Built-in Presets

Works seamlessly with YouTube videos.
Reset button to restore default settings.

Why Use YouTube Equalizer?
Tailor audio to your taste, whether you're boosting bass, enhancing treble, or fine-tuning mid-tones.

Great for music enthusiasts, content creators, and casual viewers alike. Install now and take control of your YouTube audio experience!
